{"tid":1541993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔敢跳閘嘅人 可以試一下咁樣","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:59:05.000Z","uid":112910,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"22a4041afa918c226e2c06c340a50bfb6d44f21f","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"為左保護真正跳閘既人<br />\n全世界都要全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n可能你怕俾人拉 俾人罰$500 所以你唔敢逃票 唔敢跳閘<br />\n<br />\n但係你可以用以下方法令你放心去跳<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係拍左卡之後唔好推開條棍 而係跳過去</span></span></strong><br />\n無明文規定你過閘一定要推個旋轉棍<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做啲查飛狗根本分唔到你俾左錢定係無俾<br />\n<br />\n唔同閘有唔同過法：<br />\n1.舊旋轉閘<br />\n拍完卡跳過去<br />\n2.新閘<br />\n可以用左手拍去左邊個閘 然後跳右閘<br />\n<br />\n總之做到全民跳閘<br />\n等同blackblock難以分辨"},{"pid":"ce17cdea53ea518a39e033f7c6527e9728bd1aa5","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6486d1d9ccda1636775c4fdee06d5ae76624f86f","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d689d6c7a54c3993684601f3ff228e62dcdf26d6","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cd8fb67430a55ec769cb3b7b1f19c001480134be","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"fe50d3df7e20593c5e8bfd5c9749707075d46e5b","tid":1541993,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"5/10 去到10就訓覺"},{"pid":"49bbc996805d7abbba3fd7ee58773cd8531c94ff","tid":1541993,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-t